{"tid":2165936,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府鬆懈釀禍 船員淪海上人球","createTime":"2020-08-20T06:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T06:36:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f25b7ed20d4bc7c04a20ef11a689ee5680a512d","tid":2165936,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=50f3a65d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA%2F&h=d1c2322b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港府鬆懈釀禍 船員淪海上人球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sCg0z_V083hwxdOYbu1nTUFensM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4COGOTL5LBBEXJMI3O3JW6TYPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsCg0z_V083hwxdOYbu1nTUFensM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4COGOTL5LBBEXJMI3O3JW6TYPA.jpg&h=a49eba1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■遠洋船輪機長Joanna指，相中白色建築物為船員生活區，自由活動空間有限。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情反覆，一眾船員因各國港口限制被迫漂流大海，甚至出現人道危機，有身處大海的港人船員親述離家八個月未有歸期。港府專家多次提出船員及機組人員等獲豁免檢疫組別可能是第三波疫情源頭，政府6月聲稱接受船公司要求放寬換班限制，惟未有配合加強檢疫，確保船員病毒檢測呈陰性才放行，多名船員其後染疫，其他船員滯留成為海上人球。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份滯留超過一年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nhCEnhRFH49lWL9MUJPwjuQ4IC8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UDYRNXGSJ5CBBMCWR3YCZAXS7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnhCEnhRFH49lWL9MUJPwjuQ4IC8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUDYRNXGSJ5CBBMCWR3YCZAXS7Y.jpg&h=524a0816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港船東會規管事務總監Gautam Ramaswamy<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HIniGt7qUo8Q_ofrFXRect7hwW4=/3378x1900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VJOYKHDXMRFF5KFF64JYHXMCZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHIniGt7qUo8Q_ofrFXRect7hwW4%3D%2F3378x1900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVJOYKHDXMRFF5KFF64JYHXMCZM.jpg&h=d38d6784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■載有染疫船員的貨船上月在南丫島外隔離。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n去年香港港口貨物吞吐量超過2.6億公噸，日用品、食物以至口罩等物品，大部份由船運抵港。入行約10年的首位香港女遠洋船輪機長Joanna指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據《國際海事公約》，每名船員最多只可留在船上12個月。不過，年初全球疫情大爆發後，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n遠洋船二副Leon越洋受訪，指已居於船上八個月，其間從未離開船隻，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月港府實施入境強制檢疫14日，多個類別人士包括船員可獲豁免。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自6月9日開始，港府批准所有船隻在港換班，6月30日衞生署公佈九名海外抵港船員在寧波上岸時確診，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nGautam指滯留船上的船員身心承受很大壓力，形容船員同樣站在抗疫前線，「若沒有船員全天候運送藥物醫療物資，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0f850655ef80e8e02697e38f4e0b09526cb663a6","tid":2165936,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"中國咁強大, 仲要做抗疫先鋒<br />\n揸隻船上大陸換crew囉"},{"pid":"17bbe21df0638fabb1811b1d77e352e46cd04c11","tid":2165936,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f25b7ed20d4bc7c04a20ef11a689ee5680a512d","tid":2165936,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F5IIF4S5XCJFKNB7WOP4HM34KPA%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=50f3a65d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.app